{"nodes":[{"id":"n-goal","type":"text","x":-920,"y":-260,"width":420,"height":200,"text":"# 목표\n- arXiv 논문 수집 자동화\n- AI 요약 + write-skill 문서화\n- paper/ 및 PROJECT/docs 구조 준수"},{"id":"n-source","type":"text","x":-920,"y":20,"width":420,"height":220,"text":"# 입력 소스\n- arXiv API (검색어/카테고리/기간)\n- 필수 필드: 제목, 저자, 요약, 링크, 발행일\n- 최신순/관련도/중복제거 조건 적용"},{"id":"n-collector","type":"text","x":-440,"y":20,"width":340,"height":220,"text":"# Collector\n- API 호출 및 페이지네이션\n- 메타데이터 정규화\n- 기존 문서 대비 중복 제거\n- 실패 재시도 및 로그"},{"id":"n-summarizer","type":"text","x":-40,"y":20,"width":340,"height":220,"text":"# Summarizer\n- 초록 기반 1차 요약\n- 핵심 근거/한계 추출\n- 사실/해석 분리\n- 한국어 결과 생성"},{"id":"n-writer","type":"text","x":360,"y":20,"width":420,"height":250,"text":"# Writer + $write-skill\n- paper 목적 라우팅\n- 파일명: PAPER_YYYY.MM.DD_제목.md\n- 저장 위치: paper/\n- 필수 섹션: 요약/핵심 근거/적용 메모\n- 날짜 형식: YYYY.MM.DD"},{"id":"n-output","type":"text","x":840,"y":20,"width":360,"height":210,"text":"# 산출물\n- paper/PAPER_YYYY.MM.DD_제목.md\n- 메타정보: 작성일/주제/출처\n- 품질검증: 근거 링크, 재현 가능성"},{"id":"n-docs","type":"text","x":360,"y":330,"width":420,"height":220,"text":"# 프로젝트 문서\n- PROJECT/01_paper-crawling-ai-insights/docs/\n- PRD.md\n- Architecture.canvas\n- 운영 정책/체크리스트"},{"id":"n-plan","type":"text","x":-40,"y":330,"width":340,"height":220,"text":"# 구현 계획\n1) 수집기 MVP\n2) 요약 품질 기준 확정\n3) write-skill 자동 문서 생성\n4) 중복/오류 처리 자동화\n5) 주간 점검 및 지표 리포트"},{"id":"n-prd-file","type":"file","x":840,"y":320,"width":360,"height":250,"file":"PROJECT/01_paper-crawling-ai-insights/docs/PRD.md"}],"edges":[{"id":"e1","fromNode":"n-goal","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"n-source","toSide":"top"},{"id":"e2","fromNode":"n-source","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-collector","toSide":"left"},{"id":"e3","fromNode":"n-collector","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-summarizer","toSide":"left"},{"id":"e4","fromNode":"n-summarizer","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-writer","toSide":"left"},{"id":"e5","fromNode":"n-writer","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-output","toSide":"left"},{"id":"e6","fromNode":"n-writer","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"n-docs","toSide":"top"},{"id":"e7","fromNode":"n-summarizer","fromSide":"bottom","toNode":"n-plan","toSide":"top"},{"id":"e8","fromNode":"n-docs","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-prd-file","toSide":"left"},{"id":"e9","fromNode":"n-plan","fromSide":"right","toNode":"n-docs","toSide":"left"}]}